      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Data / Schema Nodeset\n\nCandidate types from the source board:\n- `entity`\n- `field`\n- `relation`\n- `constraint`\n- `enum`\n- `schema-note`\n- `validation-rule`\n- `transform`\n- `source`\n- `mapping`\n\nThis family could become one of the most implementation-useful sets, but it also overlaps heavily with existing dictionaries, contracts, and data-flow work.",
