      "data": {
        "title": "Lock Minimal Schema Core",
        "body": "Propose `entity`, `field`, `relation`, `constraint`, `enum`, and `mapping` as the v1 core. Treat `validation-rule`, `transform`, `source`, and `schema-note` as follow-on types once the base structural model is in place.",
