      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Minimal Schema Core\n\nApprove in v1:\n- `entity`\n- `field`\n- `relation`\n- `constraint`\n- `enum`\n- `mapping`\n\nDefer:\n- `validation-rule`\n- `transform`\n- `source`\n- `schema-note`\n\nKeep v1 focused on structural modeling.",
