    {
      "id": "data-schema-dependency-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Schema Pressures",
      "position": {
        "x": 1080,
        "y": 320
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Schema Pressures\n\nLikely typed relationships:\n- `entity` contains `field`\n- `relation` connects `entity`\n- `constraint` applies to `field` or `entity`\n- `mapping` connects schema surfaces\n\nTooling pressure:\n- validation\n- schema diffing\n- code generation\n- import/export\n- interoperability with dictionary nodes\n\nStatus:\n- package root created\n- template created\n- class artifacts created\n- deferred ETL/validation types remain out of v1",
        "_classBinding": {
